        <h1>Beagle Dog</h1>
        <p>The Beagle is a small to medium-sized dog breed. It is similar in appearance to the Foxhound, but smaller with shorter legs and longer, softer ears. Beagles are popular pets due to their friendly, gentle nature and easy-going personalities.</p>
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beagle" target="_blank">Read More</a>
      </section>
